column1: Valkyrie Updated Bitcoin Futures ETF Filing Effective Date To October 20

column1: Bitcoin Price Analysis: Magnetic Technical Draw of 26677 ¡V 23 September 2023
column2: Bitcoin (BTC/USD) awaited fresh technical guidance early in the Asian session as the pair continued to trade around the 26677.10 area, a downside price objective that was easily absorbed following selling pressure that mounted around the 27393 and 27240 areas.
